<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هُمُومُ المُسْلِمِين:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>=========<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الكَاتِبُ الإِسْلاَمِيّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَاسِرُ بْنُ أَحْمَدَ بْنُ محْمُودٍ الحَمَدَاني<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>===================<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَكْثَرُ مِن <span class="c4">[١٥٠٠]</span> أَثَرٍ وَحَدِيثٍ وَبَيْتِ شِعْرٍكُلِّهَا نَادِرَة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>===============================<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أُهْدِي لِقُرَّائِي كِتَابي عَن هُمُومِ المُسْلِمِين<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لِيَكُونَ كَالسُّلْوَانِ لِلإِنْسَانِ ذِي الْقَلْبِ الحَزِين<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَلِكُلِّ مَظْلُومٍ يُعَاني أَوْ مَرِيضٍ أَوْ سَجِين<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>آثَارُهُ مخْتَارَةٌ وَكَلاَمُهُ دُرٌّ ثَمِين<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>اقْرَأْ بِهِ بَعْضَ السُّطُورِ تَجِدْ بِهَا الخَبرَ الْيَقِين<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>